        <h2>Why we created the website?</h2>
        <p>to inform about several perspectives over varied topics that in this case take over the issues of health and disease. We will go deeper into vape addiction so that our readers are able to understand the risks and consequences this devices have on our health. You can still se a video to understand why people vape, but further on we will explain and convince you why you shouldn't.</p>
